item.title: CVE-2020-10635|2024-08-04T11:06:10.438Z -- kuka -- sim%20pro
item.description: Simulation models for KUKA.Sim Pro version 3.1 are hosted by a server maintained by KUKA. When these devices request a model, the server transmits the model in plaintext.
